                "date": "2009-08-01T00:00:00Z",
                "journal": "Bioinformatics",
                "title": "The Sequence Alignment/Map format and SAMtools"
            },
            "note": "The Sequence Alignment/Map format and SAMtools.",
            "pmcid": "PMC2723002",
            "pmid": "19505943",
            "type": [
