                "date": "2021-02-16T00:00:00Z",
                "journal": "GigaScience",
                "title": "Twelve years of SAMtools and BCFtools"
            },
            "note": "Twelve years of SAMtools and BCFtools.",
            "pmcid": "PMC7931819",
            "pmid": "33590861",
            "type": [
